  <heading>SUNPKHI, SUNPKLO</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Signed unpack and extend half of vector</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction unpacks elements from the lowest or highest half of the source
vector and then sign-extends them to place in
elements of twice their size within the
destination vector.  This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
    <uses_dit condition="FEAT_SVE2 is implemented or FEAT_SME is implemented">True</uses_dit>
  </desc>
  <operationalnotes>
